        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You know that feeling when your phone rings during dinner, or while you're deep in a client meeting? That sinking realization that you're missing a potential customer — again.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've been there. Running a small business means every missed call could be a lost deal. The math is brutal: research shows that 85% of people who call a business and reach voicemail won't call back. They'll just move on to your competitor.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/what-is-ruby"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "That's exactly why I got excited about ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Ruby",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ". This virtual receptionist platform has been quietly transforming how small businesses handle communications, and their latest feature updates make it even more compelling. Let me walk you through everything that makes Ruby worth your attention.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
