      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What Ruby Actually Does (And Why It's Different)",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Ruby isn't your typical answering service. It's a hybrid system that combines real human receptionists with AI technology to handle your calls and live chats around the clock.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's what makes it special: when someone calls your business, they don't get a robotic voice or a confusing phone tree. They get a friendly, trained receptionist who answers with your company name, follows your specific instructions, and handles the call exactly how you would.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The AI component works behind the scenes — routing calls intelligently, capturing caller information, scheduling appointments, and learning your preferences over time. The result? Every caller feels like they've reached a business that genuinely cares.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/why-choose-ruby"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Want to understand the full picture? Check out our detailed guide on ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "why Ruby stands out",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " among receptionist services.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "New & Standout Features in 2025",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Ruby has rolled out several updates that significantly boost what this platform can do. Here's what caught my attention:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Enhanced AI Call Summaries",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Every call now generates a detailed, intelligent summary sent straight to your inbox or CRM. No more playing phone tag trying to figure out what the caller wanted. The AI captures names, reasons for calling, urgency levels, and any specific requests — all formatted in a way that's actually useful.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Smarter Call Routing",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The new routing engine learns your patterns. If you always take client calls but prefer sales inquiries to go to your sales team, Ruby picks up on that. It adapts based on time of day, caller history, and the nature of the call. This means fewer interruptions for you and faster service for your callers.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Live Chat Integration",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Ruby now handles live chat on your website with the same quality as phone calls. Real agents respond to visitor questions, qualify leads, and can even schedule appointments directly from chat. If you've been thinking about adding chat support but didn't want to hire someone for it, this solves that problem completely.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Bilingual Support (English & Spanish)",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For businesses serving diverse communities, Ruby's bilingual receptionists are a game-changer. Calls and chats can seamlessly switch between English and Spanish, ensuring no customer feels excluded.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Appointment Scheduling Directly in Your Calendar",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Receptionists can now book appointments directly into Google Calendar, Calendly, or other scheduling tools you already use. The caller hangs up with a confirmed appointment, and it's already on your calendar. Zero back-and-forth.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Custom Greeting Updates in Real Time",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Changed your hours? Running a special promotion? You can update your greeting script through the Ruby app instantly, and receptionists will start using it immediately. No waiting for \"the next business day\" to take effect.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
