      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Doctors, dentists, therapists, and wellness practitioners use Ruby to handle appointment scheduling, answer patient questions, and manage after-hours calls. The HIPAA-compliant features add peace of mind for sensitive industries.",
